        ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT last_verified_block_pkey
        DO UPDATE SET block_number = $1

bc4cf78d336ede903fc077884c3e618079913f07.query:
INSERT INTO withdrawals
        (
            tx_hash,
            block_number,
            token,
            amount,
            event_index_in_tx,
            status
        )
        VALUES (
            $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6
        )
        ON CONFLICT (tx_hash, block_number, event_index_in_tx) DO NOTHING

ed1a76beb8009579dd76ff79c91ede0dae66413b.query:
UPDATE withdrawals
        SET status=$1
        WHERE block_number >= $2 AND block_number <= $3
